txt.en: You are well on your way to becoming a Hero of Middle-earth. It is time to head for Bree.
'Well met, traveller. Your help is needed in Bree-town. We should speak more on the matter.'
Your experience has grown, and it is time to move forward with your training.
It is time to travel to Bree.
Talk to Second-watcher Heathstraw in Bree
Second-watcher Heathstraw awaits you near the Boar Fountain in Bree-town.\n\nYou should speak with Second-watcher Heathstraw to learn more about Bree-town.
